descriptionNullable:
This dataset contains celebrities' images and their corresponding labels for binary image classification task. The dataset has no split of train, validation, and  test folders; so, there is need to split the data for Machine Learning and Deep Learning model training process. The structure of the data is as follows:

- ROOT
   - class1:
       - live:
            - img_file;
            - img_file;
            - img_file;
            - ........
            - img_file.
       - spoof:
            - img_file;
            - img_file;
            - img_file;
            - ........
            - img_file.

   - class2:
       - live:
            - img_file;
            - img_file;
            - img_file;
            - ........
            - img_file.
       - spoof:
            - img_file;
            - img_file;
            - img_file;
            - ........
            - img_file.

...

 - classN:
       - live:
            - img_file;
            - img_file;
            - img_file;
            - ........
            - img_file.
       - spoof:
            - img_file;
            - img_file;
            - img_file;
            - ........
            - img_file.

For the image classification task, class names can be obtained from the directory names. Good luck!

